articles.author: Kevin Fagan, Annie Vainshtein
articles.title: Bob Lee murder trial: S.F. jury finds Nima Momeni guilty of second-degree murder - San Francisco Chronicle
articles.description: A San Francisco jury on Tuesday found Bay Area tech consultant Nima Momeni guilty of murdering Cash App founder and tech mogul Bob Lee.
articles.content:
Nima Momeni makes his way into the courtroom at the Hall of Justice in San Francisco. Momeni was found guilty of second-degree murder in the killing of Cash App founder Bob Lee.
